{
  "text": "Related research article Schavemaker PE, \u015a migiel WM, Poolman B. 2017. Ribosome surface properties may impose limits on the nature of the cytoplasmic proteome. eLife 6:e30084. DOI: 10.7554/eLife.30084 majority of proteins in the cytoplasm have net negative charge at physiological pH [CITATION_1] .",
